So please think
of some good ones.

00:29:07.880 --> 00:29:10.570
Don't embarrass us.

00:29:10.570 --> 00:29:15.880
So you mentioned you're
doing a sort of part two.

00:29:15.880 --> 00:29:18.760
Is this-- are you doing another
album that you're collaborating

00:29:18.760 --> 00:29:18.910
or what's in the future for you?

00:29:18.910 --> 00:29:20.285
TOM MORELLO: Yeah,
another record

00:29:20.285 --> 00:29:23.410
of diverse collaborations
that continues

00:29:23.410 --> 00:29:28.870
to try to push my guitar playing
and musical artistry further.

00:29:28.870 --> 00:29:31.540
In the same genre
of taking artists

00:29:31.540 --> 00:29:35.050
that I admire in unusual
combinations and making music

00:29:35.050 --> 00:29:37.780
that's very challenging and
exciting, but is guitar-based.

00:29:37.780 --> 00:29:38.890
DORINA ARELLANO: Cool.

00:29:38.890 --> 00:29:40.330
Looking forward to it.

