and so it jerks wildly between
Metallica's "Master of Puppets"

00:30:14.310 --> 00:30:15.750
and the "Hamilton" soundtrack.

00:30:15.750 --> 00:30:17.310
[LAUGHTER]

00:30:17.310 --> 00:30:20.440
With a good deal of clean
version Cardi B thrown in.

00:30:20.440 --> 00:30:22.126
That's what I'm-- [LAUGHS].

00:30:22.126 --> 00:30:22.974
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

